visual_description.name: cake_and_candlelit_corner.jpg
visual_description.description: A cake with icing and yellow pieces, chocolate balls with coconut, glass candle holders, doilies, candy bowls. Warm lighting, intricate wallpaper. Shadows, slight clutter.
visual_description.score_basis: The image has a cozy and inviting feel due to the warm lighting, homey wallpaper, and candlelight. However, the lighting creates some harsh shadows and there's minor clutter. Moderate sharpness, slightly uneven arrangement.
